The paper focuses on visual navigation, which is a task that involves training an embodied agent to navigate to a target object using only visual observations. This task involves elements of artificial intelligence (AI), robotics (RO), machine learning (LG), computer vision (CV), and systems and control (SY). Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.CV, and cs.SY, in that order.
